ASDG SELECTS SCALA COMPUTER TELEVISION BV AS EXCLUSIVE DISTRIBUTOR IN
THE BENELUX
 
ASDG, makers of Art Department Professional, announce that they have
selected SCALA Computer Television BV as their exclusive distributor
in the Benelux (Luxembourg, Belgium, and The Netherlands).
 
Madison WI, July 30, 1992 --- ASDG Incorporated, the leading
supplier of image processing products for the Commodore Amiga,
announce that they have selected SCALA Computer Television BV as their
exclusive distributor in the Benelux (Belgium, Luxembourg, and The
Netherlands).
 
Both companies view this relationship as a tremendous benefit to
their clients, among of whom there is a large overlapping segment.
Benelux based users of SCALA, the premier authoring and presentation
system for the Amiga, can now get ASDG products (to make their
presentation graphics look their best) from the same source.
 
To learn more about ADPro and ASDG's other color imaging solutions
(including several exciting new products about to be released),
